  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [X] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\nforge 0.1.0 (8a61027 2022-01-27T00:21:53.956016803+00:00)\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\nforge create\n\n### Operating System\n\nLinux\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nGetting the following error when trying to deploy with a Ledger Nano S:\r\n```\r\nError: \r\n   0: hidapi error: hid_error is not implemented yet\r\n\r\nLocation:\r\n   /rustc/db9d1b20bba1968c1ec1fc49616d4742c1725b4b/library/core/src/result.rs:1911\r\n```\r\nMy Ledger version info:\r\n* Secure Element: 2.1.0\r\n* Microcontroller: 1.12\r\n* Bootloader: 0.11\r\n* Ethereum app: 1.9.17",
